hey -z 60s -c 500 -q 50 http://localhost:8080/
hey -z 1m -c 100 http://localhost:8080/
hey -n 100 -c 10 http://localhost:8080/


 stick-table type ip size 1m expire 1m store http_req_rate(60s)

    http-request track-sc0 src

    acl abuse sc_http_req_rate(0) gt 100

    http-request return \
        status 429 \
        content-type application/json \
        string '{"error":"Too Many Requests"}' \
        if abuse
